title: Captain Beyond - Sufficiently Breathless (1973)
description:
From Wikipedia:

Sufficiently Breathless, the second album by Captain Beyond, was released in 1973 and features a jazzier, smoother sound than its predecessor. Original drummer Bobby Caldwell was replaced by Marty Rodriguez on this album.

Sufficiently Breathless
Bright Blue Tango
Drifting in Space
Evil Men
Starglow Energy
Distant Sun
Voyages of Past Travellers
Everything's a Circle

Lee Dorman - bass guitar 
Larry "Rhino" Reinhardt - lead guitar, acoustic guitar, slide guitar 
Rod Evans - lead and harmony vocals 
Marty Rodriguez - drums, backup vocals 
Reese Wynans - electric piano, acoustic piano 
Guille Garcia - congas, timbales, percussion 
Paul Hornsby - organ on "Starglow Energy"
